I"d<h2 id="why-are-we-doing-this">Why are we doing this?</h2>

<p>Leeds Community Homes is a Community Land Trust – and our aim is to help to create permanently affordable homes to rent and buy in Leeds.</p>

<p>We set up in 2016 – and last year we raised over £360,000 towards our first sixteen homes.  We’ve got big ambitions to build many more.</p>
